Subject: [PATCH 1311/1345] dts: a70x0: add new dts file to support comexpress
 board

commit  354b86b93ea5decfb4ad61b68952d3785b75af8f from
https://github.com/MarvellEmbeddedProcessors/linux-marvell.git

In comexpress board, SMII phy address is 0x10 instead of 0x1. This board
inherits other settings from a7020 AMC board.
This patch uses 0x10 to replace 0x1 phy address value and adds
make rule for this board dtb in makefile.

Change-Id: I98933593939ae877d4bbebbfab6a072e7778ca91
Signed-off-by: zachary zhang <zhangzg@marvell.com>
